process.name: Get UCA Listeners by Multiple Criteria

processVariable.name: UCAEventDetails

TWComponent.script: tw.local.sqlString select distinct LIMI.ID as ID, LPR.SHORT_NAME as ProjectAcronym, LPI.tip as isTip, LS.SNAPSHOT_ID as SnapshotID, LIMI.CORRELATION_STRING as Correlation, LU.IS_ENABLED as UCAEnabled, LPI.BPD_NAME as BPDName, LU.IMPLEMENTATION_TYPE as UCAImplementationType, LPI.INSTANCE_NAME as InstanceName, LPI.BPD_INSTANCE_ID as InstanceID, LPr.name as ApplicationName, LS."NAME" as snapshotName, LIMI.EVENT_ID as EventID, LU."NAME" as UCAName from lsw_uca lu, lsw_inst_msg_incl limi, lsw_project lpr, LSW_SNAPSHOT ls, LSW_BPD_INSTANCE lpi where LIMI.UCA_ID = LU.UCA_ID and LPR.PROJECT_ID = LS.PROJECT_ID and LS.SNAPSHOT_ID = LPI.SNAPSHOT_ID and LPI.BPD_INSTANCE_ID = LIMI.BPD_INSTANCE_ID and (UPPER(LPI.INSTANCE_NAME) like ? or UPPER(LPI.BPD_NAME) like ? or LPI.BPD_INSTANCE_ID = ? or UPPER(LU.name) like ? or UPPER(LPI.INSTANCE_NAME) like ?)
